WEBVTT

00:10:28.776 --> 00:10:32.735
the essence of the man,
the spirit of the man

00:10:32.759 --> 00:10:34.427
and his emotional life,

00:10:34.451 --> 00:10:37.403
and just make that the center
of the performance.

00:10:37.427 --> 00:10:40.911
AdG: Surface acting would be
mimicking Churchill's public persona.

00:10:41.347 --> 00:10:42.545
But John went deep

00:10:42.569 --> 00:10:45.490
to understand the emotional roots
of Churchill's character.

00:10:45.514 --> 00:10:47.980
JL: I was fascinated by his childhood.

00:10:48.395 --> 00:10:54.209
What a neglected, unhappy,
failure of a child he was.

00:10:55.400 --> 00:10:59.551
It helped me, sort of,
look at his entire life

00:10:59.575 --> 00:11:03.209
in terms of how he dealt with that,
how he compensated for it,